      "writtenOn": "2021-01-27T03:45:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "NoContent is HTTP 204, which I think is correct since we are not sending anything back. AFAIK Any 2xx implies success, but 204 also implies that it\u0027s expected that the response be empty. Though I don\u0027t know why NoContent(204) was chosen over Created(201).\n\nI\u0027d be interested to know what nodir@ thinks",
      "parentUuid": "4c4a83dc_f72779bc",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 105,
        "startChar": 24,
        "endLine": 105,
        "endChar": 39
