      "writtenOn": "2021-01-27T04:19:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "yes, 204 was chosen over 200 intentionally (indeed, because there is no content in response).\ngood point about 201. I don\u0027t remember why not 201, and go/resultdb-artifacts doesn\u0027t talk about it. I guess it was not considered.\n\nnote that rdb binary already expects 204 [1], so changing this to 201 would require a migration.\n\n[1]: https://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/resultdb/sink/artifact_uploader.go;l\u003d152?q\u003dresultdb%20artifact%20f:sink",
